bitonic sort (scala version)

to compile and run this application do the following:

- install the scala 2.8 compiler (on ubuntu linux e.g.  sudo apt-get install scala)
- open a termnial window and navigate to this directory
- type the following into the command line:

	scalac bitonic.scala 

(if you get compile errors, check your scala compiler version, it should be version 2.8 or newer)
	
- once the compilation is over, you can run the application by typing:

	scala bitonic.Bitonic




